text: Jameela Jamil (born 25 February 1986) is an English television and radio presenter. She hosts The Official Chart on BBC Radio 1. Jamil was born in Hampstead, London to an India father and an English mother. In 2012 the first collection by 'JAM by Jameela Jamil' was released on Very.co.uk.http://blog.very.co.uk/2012/06/the-exclusive-first-collection- designed-by-jameela-jamil-for-very-co-uk/ Jamil played Tahani on The Good Place, a sitcom that ran from 2016 to 2020.
